{"type": "article", "id": 20160, "title": "帐篷猫屋", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-04T07:40:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150628qrho05fCKMjxTIwY.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是用竹条和帆布做的猫屋，有点像一个小帐篷。几根竹条搭建了一个圆拱结构，用黄铜做连接。竹条离帆布仍有一段距离，方便手提着猫屋移动。帆布的猫屋有门和天窗，与竹条连接的地方是绿色的，有一些小的点缀和对比，自然而温暖。猫屋有 49 厘米高，售价 20304 日元，<a href=\"http://41stcentury.thebase.in/items/2237054\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买连接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150359Md4xAbZHIrwpkL0Y.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150359nZ8hVgm0NjX9uExY.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150400xm6kqQbsBoRv01tf.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150400LeHWQNJXnqcpjk10.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}